LazyTable for SwiftUI
Copyright (c) 2026 mckavan

This library is an independent SwiftUI reimplementation inspired by, and
API-compatible in spirit with, the Kotlin/Compose Multiplatform library
"lazytable" by Oleksandr Balan:

    https://github.com/oleksandrbalan/lazytable

No source code from the original project is included or derived; the layout
semantics (pinned rows/columns, footer, spans, per-axis sizing) were
re-implemented from scratch on top of SwiftUI's ScrollView.
